            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>甲骨文(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ORCL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ORCL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ORCL-US</a>)截至台北時間17日21:32股價下跌15.78美元，報297.22美元，跌幅5.04%，成交量2,346,285（股），盤中最高價304.28美元、最低價297.00美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.31%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.04%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.41%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.85%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>甲骨文(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ORCL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ORCL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ORCL-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+5.4%</li> <li>近 1 月：+2.07%</li> <li>近 3 月：+29.71%</li> <li>近 6 月：+141.21%</li> <li>今年以來：+88.52%</li></ul></section></main>",
